OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FA stepmother has been jailed for 12
OL,7,Fyears for killing a five-year-old girl
OL,8,Fby scalding her in a hot bath as a
OL,9,Fpunishment nearly half a century ago.
OL,11,FJanice Nix, 67, was sentenced at
OL,12,FIsleworth Crown Court on Friday for
OL,13,Fthe manslaughter of Andrea Bernard in
OL,14,FThornton Heath, south London, in 1978.
OL,16,FAndrea's death had been treated as an
OL,17,Faccident until her older brother
OL,18,FDesmond Bernard went to police in 2022
OL,19,Fwith a new account of what happened,
OL,20,Fthe trial previously heard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FNix, a retired probation officer, was
OL,7,Falso sentenced for cruelty against Mr
OL,8,FBernard between October 1975 and June
OL,9,F1978, when he was seven-to-nine years
OL,10,Fold.
OL,12,FMr Justice Nicholas Lavender,
OL,13,Fsentencing, told the defendant: "I'm
OL,14,Fsure that you ran the bath, you knew
OL,15,Fhow hot it was, you told Andrea to get
OL,16,Fin the bath, she said it was too hot,
OL,17,Fbut you either put her in the bath or
OL,18,Fmade her get into it.
OL,20,F"And you heard her screams," the judge
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,26,@uD@aOU|D@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
