OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,F"At the very least the risk ought to
OL,7,Fhave been obvious to you."
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FNix, who sat in the dock dressed in a
OL,15,Fwhite shirt and a black blazer jacket
OL,16,Fand trousers, cried through most of
OL,17,Fthe hearing and wept loudly while the
OL,18,Fjudge read his remarks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
