PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement he read
OL,7,Fout in court, Mr Bernard said the
OL,8,Fabuse he and his sister suffered `
OL,9,Fwhich involved beatings with a belt
OL,10,Fand being forced to eat cat food ` led
OL,11,Fto Andrea's death and left him
OL,12,F"broken".
OL,14,F"The last memories I have of my
OL,15,Fsister's life are piercing screams and
OL,16,Flying about her death to survive," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FHe then addressed Nix directly,
OL,20,Fsaying: "You took away her future and
OL,21,Fchanged mine forever.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@HO]vD@AOUxD@bO]|D@IOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,F"Your contrived grief at Andrea's
OL,7,Ffuneral, the lies, the tears. You
OL,8,Ffooled my family because they couldn't
OL,9,Fimagine the unimaginable.
OL,11,F"You took their kindness for weakness
OL,12,Fand you manipulated them so that you
OL,13,Fcouldn't be found out.
OL,15,F"The time has come for you to
OL,16,Facknowledge what you have done to
OL,17,FAndrea and myself."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
