CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FProsecutor Kerry Broome read out the
OL,7,Fstatement of Angela Bernard, Desmond
OL,8,Fand Andrea's mother, which described
OL,9,Fthe little girl as "so sweet and
OL,10,Floving".
OL,12,F"When she died, it completely
OL,13,Fdestroyed me," the statement read.
OL,14,F"She deserved to have a life, not be
OL,15,Flying around in a cemetery. I think
OL,16,Fabout her every single day."
OL,18,FOn June 6 1978, Nix was "furious"
OL,19,Fafter Andrea ignored instructions not
OL,20,Fto leave the house and to help clean
OL,21,Finstead.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@GO]tD@AOUuD@NO]vD@AOUxD@\O]zD@
OL,26,AYOUzD@aO]
