OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FNix, then called Janice Thomas and in
OL,7,Fher late teenage years, had been in a
OL,8,Frelationship with the children's
OL,9,Ffather, also named Desmond Bernard,
OL,10,Fand was in effect their stepmother,
OL,11,Fthe court heard.
OL,13,FShe shouted at Andrea in an "extremely
OL,14,Floud" voice before beating her, the
OL,15,Ftrial was told.
OL,17,FMr Bernard, giving evidence, told
OL,18,Fjurors he later heard the bath running.
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
