PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FHe went on: "I could hear Janice
OL,7,Fshouting: 'Get in the bath', and I
OL,8,Fcould hear Andrea saying: 'The bath is
OL,9,Ftoo hot, mummy.'
OL,11,F"I could hear Janice shouting: 'Get in
OL,12,Fthe bath, get in the bath', and then I
OL,13,Fheard screaming and splashing.
OL,15,F"Then I heard the screaming stopped
OL,16,Fand I could hear Janice calling Andrea
OL,17,Fto 'wake up, wake up'."
OL,19,FMr Bernard said he then entered the
OL,20,Fbathroom and saw Nix cradling Andrea,
OL,21,Fwho was "limp" and wrapped in a towel.
OL,26,@nD@MOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@WO]}D@IOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
