PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FHe added: "I could see skin falling
OL,7,Foff her."
OL,9,FAsked whether Nix said anything, Mr
OL,10,FBernard replied: "She asked me to say
OL,11,Fit was an accident... and to say that
OL,12,Fwe were in the garden when it happened
OL,13,Fand that she would never beat me
OL,14,Fagain."
OL,16,FAndrea died nearly six weeks after
OL,17,Farriving at hospital with burns to 50%
OL,18,Fof her body, the court heard.
OL,26,@nD@KOUoD@IO]rD@ROUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
