PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FA burns expert told the trial that a
OL,7,Fchild exposed to water hot enough to
OL,8,Fcause Andrea's injuries would
OL,9,Finstinctively try to get out by
OL,10,Fstanding up, not remain seated.
OL,12,FProsecutors argued this meant Nix must
OL,13,Fhave forcibly held parts of Andrea's
OL,14,Fbody underwater.
OL,16,FDuring the 1978 inquest investigation,
OL,17,FNix had initially claimed Andrea took
OL,18,Fa bath on her own and later complained
OL,19,Fof itchy legs before fainting, jurors
OL,20,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FBut she admitted during her trial to
OL,7,Fgiving a false account of the events
OL,8,Fto the coroner because she was "in a
OL,9,Fpanic" over having failed to supervise
OL,10,FAndrea while she took a bath.
OL,12,FDuring a 2022 police interview, Nix
OL,13,Fgave a version of events that differed
OL,14,F"significantly" from her original
OL,15,Fstatement from the time, having not
OL,16,Fbeen told that investigators had found
OL,17,Fit, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@FO]vD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FShe also claimed that the coroner
OL,7,Ffound Andrea's death was because of an
OL,8,Foverheated bath caused by a faulty
OL,9,Fboiler ` something not mentioned in
OL,10,Fthe report.
OL,12,FThe year before the police
OL,13,Finvestigation was launched, Nix
OL,14,Fpublished a book on her life titled
OL,15,FBreaking Out and written with
OL,16,FElizabeth Sheppard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
