PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781916478
OL,3,CStepmother jailed for manslaughter of
OL,4,Cgirl in scalding bath in 1978
OL,6,FIn the book, Nix told the story of how
OL,7,Fshe went from being a major drug
OL,8,Fdealer dubbed "Mama J" to turning her
OL,9,Flife around and becoming an award-
OL,10,Fwinning probation officer.
OL,12,FThe defendant, of Clapham, south
OL,13,FLondon, worked for the Probation
OL,14,FService between 2014 and 2019 and won
OL,15,Fthe Probation Service's diversity and
OL,16,Fengagement award in 2015.
OL,18,FShe had previously served two
OL,19,F"substantial" terms of imprisonment
OL,20,Ffor drugs offences, the court was told.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@VO]{D@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
